15:T44f,Internal evidence clearly identifies this as a knee implant product family with advanced TiNbN coating technology. The brochure description provides specific technical differentiators (2x harder than oxidized zirconium, 8x harder than Cobalt Chrome). The 'OPULENT Gold' naming suggests this is a premium-tier product within the OPULENT knee portfolio. However, brand field is empty and no external verification is available. Classification is clinically sound based on internal evidence but requires review for: (1) confirmation of manufacturer (Meril Life Sciences appears in current_classification but not verified), (2) validation of coating performance claims, (3) clarification of whether 'Gold' refers to color/appearance or premium positioning, (4) confirmation this is the complete system vs. component-specific coating offering. Entity type is product_family as this represents a complete knee replacement system line with proprietary coating technology, not just a single implant component. Recommend send_to_review for brand validation and marketing claims verification before public display.7:["$","div",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-[#0A0A0A] text-white","children":[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org/\",\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"OPULENT Gold Knee\",\"description\":\"Advanced knee implant featuring OPULENT TiNbN coating technology with superior hardness and abrasion resistance compared to conventional materials\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"Meril\"},\"category\":\"Knee Implants\",\"manufacturer\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Meril Life Sciences\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateOffer\",\"offerCount\":\"1\",\"lowPrice\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"INR\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\"}}"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-24","children":[["$","nav",null,{"className":"flex mb-10 tex